    • determineAllPossibleApplications

      Set<RuleApplication> determineAllPossibleApplications(PhysicalPlan plan)
      Returns all possible applications of this rule for the given plan. Each of the returned RuleApplication objects will return the given plan when calling RuleApplication.getPlan() and it will return this rule when calling RuleApplication.getRule().
